        14993
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Verify the resource works with a credential specified for Get, Set and Test",
      "pos": [
        14998,
        15073
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If your resource accesses shares, test all the variants you need to support.",
      "pos": [
        15079,
        15155
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example:",
      "pos": [
